KEY LEARNING:

Distribution Group vs Shared Mailbox:
- Distribution Group: Send 1 email to many people (each gets copy)
- Shared Mailbox: Multiple people manage ONE inbox together

Mail Flow Rules work with SHARED MAILBOXES, not distribution groups.

